@nikkikphillips  looking at your photo on the blog looks like my skin now. My journey to remove pigmentation started about 6 years ago and up till last July nearly gone. But a different laser treatment , I usually have BBL. or RUBY LASER. , totally caused one patch on my cheek to resurface. Since then it's been a constant battle with a few different treatments. IPL  made a slight difference. Sadly I read something today that said beware all these treatments can make it worse.  I'm actually about to start on a short course of hydroquinone to see if it will fade. Then hit it again with laser. But it's so frustrating.

Yes love IPL, it's the best. I'm having a session soon, works so well. P.s see you at the JFJ shoot 🌽
